name: Millennium-Eyes Restrict
desc:
"Relinquished" + 1 Effect Monster
Once per turn, when an opponent's monster activates its effect (Quick Effect): You can target 1 Effect Monster your opponent controls or in their GY; equip that target to this card. Gains ATK and DEF equal to the combined ATK and DEF of the monsters equipped to it by this effect. Monsters with the same name as a monster equipped to this card by this effect cannot attack, also negate their effects.
